pageContext.claim: “Likewise, Representative Ilhan Omar is going to be very much involved in a Biden government.They will put this hate-filled America-bashing socialist front and center in deciding the fate of your family and deciding the fate of your country. She would like to make the government of our country just like the country from where she came, Somalia, no government, no safety, no police, no nothing, just anarchy.”
pageContext.analysis: There is no evidence to support this. The Biden campaign has kept its distance from Rep. Omar. In fact, she announced she believes Tara Reade, a former U.S. Senate staffer who has leveled sexual assault allegations against Biden, but she said she would still vote for him over Trump.
